exif.description: Operation Mountain Viper put the soldiers of A Company, 2nd Battalion 22nd Infantry Division, 10th Mountain in the Afghanistan province of Daychopan to search for Taliban and or weapon caches that could be used against U.S. and allied forces. Soldiers quickly walk to the ramp of the CH-47 Chinook cargo helicopter that will return them to Kandahar Army Air Field.  (U.S. Army photo by Staff Sgt. Kyle Davis) (Released)
El cielo sobre Berlin (Heaven above Berlin)
